<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ankehitriny, Jereo, ry Ray! FFPM296</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ankehitriny
 Jereo ry Ray !
 Ny mpivahiny
 Miampy indray ;
 Ka manomeza hery
 Ny fiangonanao,
 Mba tsy hiasa irery
 Ny olonao.

[V2]
 Avia hitahy
 Ny olonao ;
 Ka ny Fanahy
 Omeonao ;
 Ho hery izay handrava
 Ny toetra ratsinay,
 Ho jiro hanazava
 Ny lalana.

[V3]
 Ry Tompo tia !
 Tarihonao
 Hifankatia
 Ny olonao,
 Mba tsy ho rava intsony
 Ny fikambananay,
 Hamantana ao ambony
 Ny dianay.</lyrics>
<author>P.P. Bliss</author>
<hymn_number>296</hymn_number>
</song>